Core features:

 * Additional RSS fields (guid, pubDate, source, lastBuildDate, language...)

 * Default language when Accept-Language is not set at all

 * Browsing support for long lists (forward/backward movement)

 * Published/unpublished content

 * Independent language and filtering in WMI?

 * Support for enabled/disabled actions

 * Save the exported HTML for structured text content in DB

 * Authentication and acces rights management

 * Content management controls outside wmi (when authorized)

 * Change log and Last-Modified HTTP header support

 * Locking

 * META tags pointing to language variants

 * Print preview

 * Support multithreaded Apache MPM (currently broken).


Extensions:

 * Articles

 * Image galeries

